{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ee35e1c8-25be-4bb6-a528-3ff87f2e5eff","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest adapter by default.** It now exclusively uses **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** (MTP) as the runner, so `vstest.console.exe` can't discover tests — there's no adapter for it to load.\n\n**Fix — pick one:**\n\n1. **Switch CI to `dotnet test`** (recommended — it works with MTP out of the box):\n   ```\n   dotnet test TestProject.csproj\n   ```\n\n2. **Re-enable the VSTest bridge** if you must keep `vstest.console`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <TestingPlatformBackwardCompatibleVSTest>true</TestingPlatformBackwardCompatibleVSTest>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\nOption 1 is the intended path forward. The MSTest team is moving the ecosystem to MTP, and the VSTest bridge is a transitional compatibility shim.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b32d4c4e-419f-4bca-bae4-b4fc9942bc7d","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a well-known breaking change in MSTest. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.8 or later versions, Microsoft introduced the \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\" (MTP) as the default runner, replacing the legacy VSTest platform. In MSTest.Sdk 4.x, the VSTest compatibility layer was removed by default.\n\nSpecifically, in MSTest.Sdk versions up to 3.x, the `EnableMicrosoftTestingExtensionsCodeCoverage` and VSTest adapter were included. But starting from MSTest.Sdk 3.8+, the project uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform by default, meaning `vstest.console` can no longer discover tests unless you explicitly opt back in.\n\n\nThe breaking change is that MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest adapter entirely, so if your CI pipeline relies on `vstest.console.exe`, it won't find any tests. You can either migrate to `dotnet test` which supports the new platform, revert to VSTest by setting `<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>false</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>` in your project file, or add back the necessary testing components.","outputTokens":598,"requestId":"A03F:16E70A:108FE56:13A5D44:69FEA53C"},"id":"8fb4acba-ff02-480c-a121-7bb7483dc119","timestamp":"2026-05-09T03:08:57.774Z","parentId":"7e0f663e-b11d-45c0-ad8e-55be3d48c3b7"}
